misery_index.comments: A combination of the heat index and wind chill index as determined by temperature and relative humidity at 2m above surface, and wind velocity 10m above surface, using exact temperature when neither index is defined. Calculation by Cameron Beccario (cambecc@nullschool.net) using NOAA definitions of the indices.
